{"tid":2125831,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"全新金牛座吹水活動打機tg谷","createTime":"2020-07-26T12:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T00:51:52.000Z","uid":217514,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"00c5559feeb9351beaedde251ae67f61188db79e","tid":2125831,"uid":217514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:43:31.000Z","msg":"《性格保守且沈穩的金牛座男生，如同歸隱詩人般追求安穩恬靜的田園生活。》<br />\n《八面玲瓏的金牛座女生，恰到好處的交際手腕總能贏得眾人的好感。》<br />\n<br />\n金牛座不嬲都唔係好多人理解到㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身為金牛座嘅你嚟圍爐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然大家都未必係星座撚 但主要想搵返同星座嘅人嚟吹水<br />\n仲可以搞下生日聚添<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然都歡迎想溝金牛座仔仔/女女嘅你嚟問下各位大師如何入手<br />\n<br />\n依個谷乜都吹得 唔歡迎藍絲呀！明㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n活動都會搞 想乜聚有乜聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對狗公娘娘表示強烈不了 你做咩都會有人知㗎<br />\n當然你要扮你喺金牛都唔緊要 只係無乜意思～<br />\n其他星座jj有意入嚟分享你嘅故事求救好歡迎㗎！<br />\n<br />\n間唔時會清人 有意入嚟就填form<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/S5mp1GyocoSDZdNk7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FS5mp1GyocoSDZdNk7&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=467833d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/S5mp1GyocoSDZdNk7</a>"},{"pid":"207115f531166a4414cf6102bcf0d0363e7035fb","tid":2125831,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T12:57:05.000Z","msg":"全新？？？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZ120mY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZ120mY.png&h=7a18075e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"267b7393010cfd19c5a7c654897c2e52bbb65fc8","tid":2125831,"uid":217514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T17:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1c6c05a1f2ec4da8d1242888603ba2c362866b","